               <item n="project_comment_old">&lt;p&gt;Theres' English Translation:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;table class='table_lines'&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;a2&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;... to be boiled ... to be placed ...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;a3&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;... || Patchouly, cassia bark, ...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;a4&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Trigonella corniculata, Tabernaemontana coronaria, ... one equal (measure) ... Ficus indica ||&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;a5&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;The three myrobalans, honey, pink water-lily, safran threads, ...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;a6&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;of ferruginous earth ... alcohol of ... Then ...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;b1&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;... are to be made, one measure of medicaments with sesame oil&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;b2&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;is to be made [put?] on[to] the head, ..., destroys the &lt;i&gt;pärsare&lt;/i&gt;, Clerodendron siphonantus, honey [or sandalwood?]&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;b3&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;white lotus root, dill, sugar, ...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;b4&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;... sesame, (of) all this one measure ...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;b5&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;..., ... is ... this poultice ...&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[[Broomhead I]]: 38 has transliteration and notes containing the following translations: &lt;br&gt;
a2 is to be cooked ... is not to be placed &lt;br&gt;
a3 (this oil) is called taila. &lt;br&gt;
a6 iron-rust ... rice-brandy is to be added [to this]. Thereupon &lt;br&gt;
b1 ... is to be done ... are to be done in the same quantity, the remedies. Oil of sesame &lt;br&gt;
b2 is to be applied on the head [and this] banishes the vertigo and destroys headaches. &lt;br&gt;
b4 ground sesame &lt;br&gt;
b5 ... the skin ... becomes ...: This pill&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Bild (so vorhanden), Transliteration und Transkription müssen überprüft werden! –Hannes (Fri, 2018-08-03, 17:46:50 (CEST))</item>
